d numerical data. Two challenging problems having a wide range\nof material properties and complex dynamics are conducted to demonstrate the\ncapability of the proposed model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Feb 2021 05:34:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Feb 2021 01:58:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2021 16:14:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-16"}
