tion with time we were\nable to generate quantitative insights into the time scales involved in the\nthermalisations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Feb 2021 08:02:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Apr 2021 14:58:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
